title: UEFA Champions League group stage results & scorers (2nd matchday) - World
text:

Scorers: Costa 13, Lewandowski 21, 28, 58, Goetze 25
Group G
FC Porto 2-1 Chelsea

Maccabi Tel Aviv 0-2 Dynamo Kyiv

Group H
Lyon 0-1 Valencia
Scorer: Feghouli 42

Scorers: Dzyuba 35, Shatov 67 / Matton 56

Group A
Malmo FF 0-2 Real Madrid
Scorer: Ronaldo 29, 90
Shakhtar Donetsk 0-3 Paris Saint Germain
Scorers: Aurier 7, Ibrahimovic 65, 90
Group B
CSKA Moscow 3-2 PSV Eindhoven

Group C
